{"id":268243,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-贵州唐诗强为保农田入狱，妻子被禁深山/","date":"2012-12-14T05:46:27Z","modified":"2012-12-14T05:46:27Z","title":"维权网 | 贵州唐诗强为保农田入狱，妻子被禁深山逼签字（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员陈华报道）贵州省桐梓县燎原镇大关村唐诗强，为了保护农田，反对强征土地，并拒绝在征地协议上签字，被逮捕入狱。经过四次开庭，桐梓县法院最终以妨害公务罪判处唐诗强有期徒刑两年半。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>，唐诗强向遵义市中级法院提起再审，至今无任何回复。妻子令狐荣先</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>被镇书记王国燕以及杨小勇、谭桥、杨名强、唐淑亮、旁观廷、夏天勇绑架至贵州息烽深山一岩壁下，胁迫签订《土地买卖协议》，《上访终止协议》。随后，被带回家中，全天候跟踪监视。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>燎原镇是贵州省唯一的高原上的平原，面积</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">83</span><span>平方公里。因其形状酷似葫芦，故称葫芦坝，一条大河穿坝而过。过去，葫芦坝常遭水灾。自清朝道光三年，各任知县就筹款进行开河泄水工程。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1952</span><span>年以来，历届政府投入巨资，进行水利工程建设。修建了长</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>公里</span><span>的天门河大渠。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1978</span><span>年，中铁二局修建了排洪隧道开挖工程。至此，葫芦坝成为水稻亩产</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1600</span><span>斤以上，油菜</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span>斤以上的丰产坝，良田近两万亩。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年，燎原镇被规划为蟠龙工业园区。从此，贵州遵义金兰、伟明铝业公司、贵州国产电子产业公司等不断的蚕食基本农田。至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年，燎原镇近两万亩良田被蚕食殆尽。昔日的稻菽万重浪，被一个个烟囱取代。村民唐诗强、侯光义、令狐昌永、令狐荣先、李忠孝、舒明学等人对政府的行径进行了坚决抵制，特别是唐诗强，为征地不签字不领款，要求政府拿出国务院批文。于是，镇长罗礼万、书记王国燕就对唐诗强栽赃陷害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年底，一家外地建房户无权卖房而将房卖了，唐诗强与当地村民就将此住户房屋两边道路挖了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>的大年三十，派出所警察娄小丽、粟立鹏、胡琪来到唐诗强家，不出示任何证件，就一把抓住唐诗强的衣领说：“走，到派出所一趟”。村民们见状，纷纷围了过来，说：“这是村里的事，要去大家一起去”。这时，隔壁妇女娄金树拿着一瓶刚兑好的奶粉走了过来，一不小心，奶水被挤了出来弄脏了娄小丽的衣服。指导员娄小丽一把抓住娄金树的头发，将其头按在门角上。娄金树的丈夫唐书现挥着拳头冲了过来，但没打人。村民们将娄小丽、粟立鹏、胡琪轰出屋外。娄小丽打电话，请求县公安局支援。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>分钟后，来了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>个警察，了解情况后就走了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>事隔</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">46</span><span>天后的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点钟，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>个警察带着一只警犭，来到唐诗强家，说：“跟我们走一趟”，谁知，刚出门，唐诗强就被手铐铐住。当晚被抓捕的还有令狐荣先、唐书回等十几人，且没有出示任何证件。派出所长顾明权打电话给燎原镇书记王国燕说：“最多拘留几天，你要抓他们，就把材料送过来”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，桐梓县公安局对令狐荣先行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天，唐诗强送看守所羁押。镇书记王国燕对唐诗强说：“你把字签了，我就向公安局求情，放你出来。”唐诗强断然拒绝。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>，桐梓县公安局以桐公（刑）逮字﹝</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>﹞</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">75</span><span>号，对唐诗强进行逮捕。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>，桐梓县法院以妨害公务罪对唐诗强进行审判，因证明无罪的材料太多，无法宣判。随后又进行了两次开庭，仍无法宣判。到了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日</span><span>，法院强行判决唐诗强有期徒刑两年半。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>，唐诗强上诉至遵义市中级法院，被驳回维持原判，但未开庭。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>，唐诗强再次向中级法院提起再审。直到现在，遵义市中级法院未作任何回复。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在此期间，唐诗强的妻子令狐荣先，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>五次到国家信访局、中纪委、国土资源部、公安部上访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，令狐荣先从北京被截访回来后，镇书记王国燕以及杨小勇、谭桥、杨名强、唐淑亮、旁观廷、夏天勇将令狐荣先绑架至贵州息烽深山一岩壁下，胁迫签订《土地买卖协议》、《上访终止协议》。镇书记王国燕说：“如果不签字，就送你到看守所，关押两年半，还要骚扰你读高中的儿子”。经过两天的软禁，令狐荣先为了儿子，被迫签了字。随后，令狐荣先被带回家受到全天候的跟踪监视。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-IVMcHqbjd6Y/UMqeP3nLlQI/AAAAAAAAWcM/gy4fQG7-qYs/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE04.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"222\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-IVMcHqbjd6Y/UMqeP3nLlQI/AAAAAAAAWcM/gy4fQG7-qYs/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE04.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-eBrDxvAVvr0/UMqeQ1C5D3I/AAAAAAAAWcQ/c7m-R9uG24M/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE03.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"210\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-eBrDxvAVvr0/UMqeQ1C5D3I/AAAAAAAAWcQ/c7m-R9uG24M/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE03.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2QX7-Cloudk/UMqeSV21OHI/AAAAAAAAWcc/C7fKQL1wfgw/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2QX7-Cloudk/UMqeSV21OHI/AAAAAAAAWcc/C7fKQL1wfgw/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"231\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-gMt-orW-AF8/UMqeT746BXI/AAAAAAAAWcg/2hwSVyxZFoo/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-gMt-orW-AF8/UMqeT746BXI/AAAAAAAAWcg/2hwSVyxZFoo/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE01.jpg\" width=\"234\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-O9JibzCl5zA/UMqeVA2H-mI/AAAAAAAAWco/kclqcYuOWBc/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE02.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-O9JibzCl5zA/UMqeVA2H-mI/AAAAAAAAWco/kclqcYuOWBc/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE02.jpg\" width=\"253\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4957417751908845262?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}